  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/19/office-remote-for-windows-phone/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/6dfbb4fe70af17b0de0e61a4eec70402/office-remote-windows-phone.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n虽说微软一直在标榜 Windows Phone 中所整合的 Office 功能，但长久以来我们在这个平台上并没有看到过任何来自官方的 Office 套件遥控应用。现在微软终于意识到了这一点，并于今日针对 Windows Phone 8 用户上架了 Office Remote。这款软件能帮助使用者遥控 Windows 7 或 Windows 8 电脑（需支持蓝牙）上的 Excel、PowerPoint、Word，让简报过程变得更方便一些。目前该应用已在 Marketplace 中上线，下次用最新的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/lumia1520\">Lumia 1520</a> 来试试吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/11/18/office-remote-for-windows-phone/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://thenextweb.com/microsoft/2013/11/18/microsoft-launches-office-remote-windows-phone-app-control-office-2013-office-365-documents-pc/?awesm=tnw.to_j0jl6&amp;utm_source=Twitter&amp;utm_campaign=social%20media&amp;utm_medium=Spreadus\" target=\"_blank\">The Next Web</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/store/app/office-remote/01f53e5a-7870-49cb-8afc-d6fab6d7a3cd\" target=\"_blank\">Windows Phone Store</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/19/office-remote-for-windows-phone/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20771232/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/19/office-remote-for-windows-phone/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
